Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:45.22,Background,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you want to play him in an even game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:46.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can make it happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.60,Sai,,0,0,0,,'I wonder'!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.67,0:01:56.47,Sai,,0,0,0,,But Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:02:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it happen someday. Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.00,Sai,,0,0,0,,When is this 'someday'?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,'Someday' is 'someday'.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it was an important match for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't play it because of\Nyour selfishness, don't you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.04,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it was your fault for coming to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.19,Sai,,0,0,0,,Torajirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,He was a very clever...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.80,Sai,,0,0,0,,and truly kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you're saying is\Nthat I'm stupid and unkind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.81,0:02:42.72,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:52.03,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(285,115)}The Fiftieth Match
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:52.03,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Sai of the Fujiwara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,Why did God...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:05.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,revive me in Hikaru's mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:11.99,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's true that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.10,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru is growing very quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:20.24,Sai,,0,0,0,,and it brings me both\Npride and joy in teaching him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:22.52,Sai,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:23.85,Sai,,0,0,0,,what about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.74,Sai,,0,0,0,,what about my Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:40.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,I hate this existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.91,Sai,,0,0,0,,The chance to play him finally came...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:52.61,Sai,,0,0,0,,the game against him when I was\Nsupposed to master the divine move...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:56.97,Sai,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.16,Sai,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:03.13,Sai,,0,0,0,,In a game that I couldn't play as myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.23,0:04:09.17,Sai,,0,0,0,,I couldn't head for that divine height with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.44,Sai,,0,0,0,,If I cannot master the divine move...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.97,Sai,,0,0,0,,why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.93,Sai,,0,0,0,,How long am I supposed to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.27,Sai,,0,0,0,,A thousand years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.82,Sai,,0,0,0,,Everything began from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,Every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.25,Sai,,0,0,0,,I played Go within the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.22,Sai,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.20,Sai,,0,0,0,,when I played the other tutor that His Majesty had,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:04.08,Sai,,0,0,0,,in a match to decide who would\Nbecome the only tutor for His Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:21.95,Sai,,0,0,0,,he placed a white stone that\Nwas hidden among his stones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:26.11,Sai,,0,0,0,,in his Agehama during a moment\Nwhen everyone else was distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.54,Sai,,0,0,0,,When I tried to raise my voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.31,Sai,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:32.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:34.41,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You! You just placed a black stone\Nfrom your Goke into your Agehama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.70,Sai,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,That is what you just did!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a stupid excuse that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.91,Background,,0,0,0,,You just placed a black stone that was\Nhidden in your Goke into your Agehama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:54.00,Background,,0,0,0,,when everyone's attention was on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.94,Sai,,0,0,0,,You are the one making excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.80,Background,,0,0,0,,Stop it. Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not wish to even consider that such\Na dishonest act has occurred before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.93,Sai,,0,0,0,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:15.89,Sai,,0,0,0,,I could not contain my anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.57,Sai,,0,0,0,,I was charged with cheating during the game
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.25,Sai,,0,0,0,,and driven out of the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:26.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,I no longer had a reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.68,Sai,,0,0,0,,Two days after the match...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.19,Sai,,0,0,0,,I drowned myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:39.62,Sai,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:43.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,I wanted to play Go a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:48.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,My soul, unable to find peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.68,Sai,,0,0,0,,possessed a Go board,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.43,0:06:52.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,and after a long period of time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:55.94,Sai,,0,0,0,,heard a voice of a young boy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.87,Sai,,0,0,0,,on Innoshima, within the sea of Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:03.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,Torajirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:06.79,Memory,,0,0,0,,Young boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.49,Memory,,0,0,0,,if you can see the tears of grief that I shed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:15.21,Memory,,0,0,0,,let me dwell in a corner of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:22.53,Sai,,0,0,0,,I was able to play Go as much\Nas I wished, together with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:28.19,Sai,,0,0,0,,He changed his name to Shuusaku, and\Nbecame the successor to the Honinbou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:33.75,Sai,,0,0,0,,I believed that I would be able to\Nmaster the divine move together with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.69,Sai,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.35,Sai,,0,0,0,,he could not defeat disease and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:47.61,Sai,,0,0,0,,Torajirou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.65,Sai,,0,0,0,,Honinbou Shuusaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:55.74,Sai,,0,0,0,,I will never forget the time that I spent with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:07:59.38,Sai,,0,0,0,,Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.04,Background,,0,0,0,,Sai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how you want to play it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:09.68,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:13.48,Sai,,0,0,0,,and then you appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.75,Background,,0,0,0,,This stain just won't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.32,Background,,0,0,0,,There's no stain. It's clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:24.95,Background,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:28.03,Background,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing. Where!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.61,Sai,,0,0,0,,Can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.69,Background,,0,0,0,,That's what I've been saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:38.70,Sai,,0,0,0,,Can you hear my voice!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.72,Sai,,0,0,0,,You can hear my voice, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.13,Sai,,0,0,0,,The gods before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:54.59,Sai,,0,0,0,,I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.56,Sai,,0,0,0,,Now I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,I can return to the present world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:05.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:22.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.07,Sai,,0,0,0,,I was concerned at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:29.68,Sai,,0,0,0,,After all, Hikaru, you had never played Go before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You like Go that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:32.64,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You still want to play Go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:34.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad, I have no intentions of playing Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, can't you possess someone other than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.26,Sai,,0,0,0,,Probably not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.80,Background,,0,0,0,,Fine, I guess it would be\Nokay to play once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.65,Sai,,0,0,0,,And!? And!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.89,0:10:11.34,Sai,,0,0,0,,Where are we playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.72,Background,,0,0,0,,In a Go Salon.
