Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:18.44,Background,,0,0,0,,When there are two Yose spots\Nleft, how would you play, Yuuki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:19.19,Background,,0,0,0,,Here.
