Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.32,0:00:03.70,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,On this eye, this eye on yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.33,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,everything will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:15.06,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,I will tell apart the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:26.96,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,How many dreams did we carry with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:30.46,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,through this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:33.81,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,We gave them all a try, even as we cried
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:37.28,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,wandering around so very lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:44.64,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,Even then, I will find a deciding move,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:53.64,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,just as good as anyone else's, and take hold of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:57.19,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,On this eye, this eye of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.19,0:01:00.72,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,everything will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:07.86,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,I'll tell apart, just the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:11.23,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,Even if the truth is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.94,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,so harsh it's suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:18.44,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:23.87,Op2English2,,0,0,0,,in a place like this.
