Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:52.84,Ed4English,,0,0,0,,How many sad memories did we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:58.00,Ed4English,,0,0,0,,What kind of happy days are we going to
